
Google login integration

1. Create a Project:
   Open Google developer console
   create new project
   Enter the name for your project ex. 'GoogleLogin' or anything and click on "create".

2. Enable APIs and Services:
   In Enable APIs and Services search for Google+ api and select it.
   Click the "Enable" button. 

3. Create OAuth 2.0 credentials: 
   In Google developer console go to "credential" in left sidebar.
   click "create Credentials" and select "OAuth client ID" and click "Configure consent screen".
   choose 'external' and create
   complete the process.
   again In Google developer console go to "credential" in left sidebar.
   click "create Credentials" and select "OAuth client ID".
   select "web application"